<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.8">
<l>kaccoṭu poṟcurikai kāmpu kaṉakavaḷai</l>
<l>yucci maṇiccuṭṭi yoṇtāḷ niraippoṟpū</l>
<l>vaccuta ṉukkeṉ ṟavaṉiyāḷ pōttantāḷ</l>
<l>naccu mulaiyuṇṭāy tālēlō nārāya ṇāvaḻēl tālēlō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lady Earth sent “for Acyuta” knife of gold along with a belt,</l>
<l>silk cloth, a golden bracelet, a sapphire head ornament,</l>
<l>and golden flowers in a row for [your] bright feet.</l>
<l>You who drank the poison breast, tālēlō! Nārāyaṇa, do not cry, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
